practically nothing.

323
00:16:25,439 --> 00:16:26,526
Costume change.

324
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:28,615
This is my closet.

325
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:33,607
The original tenants
laid the last brick

326
00:16:33,725 --> 00:16:35,392
