this place up for a sheckle.

334
00:16:55,215 --> 00:16:56,225
Well, it is...

335
00:16:57,227 --> 00:16:59,752
Crowded, but that might have
something to do with the sale,

336
00:16:59,928 --> 00:17:02,453
which means that if we're successful

337
00:17:02,557 --> 00:17:04,341
you're gonna lose
the customers you have

338
