raising prices.

340
00:17:08,433 --> 00:17:10,128
Can you imagine what my father said?

341
00:17:10,476 --> 00:17:12,178
Well, you do have
to give them something

342
00:17:12,308 --> 00:17:13,668
for their higher dollar counts.

343
00:17:13,808 --> 00:17:14,808
It's just...

344
00:17:15,514 --> 00:17:17,510
Awfully hard to define what that is.

345
00:17:23,871 --> 00:17:24,871
How may I help you?

346
00:17:25,556 --> 00:17:27,160
I make them say that.

347
00:17:27,680 --> 00:17:29,523
Carol, can we see
this tray right here?

348
00:17:38,682 --> 00:17:39,682
Sea horses,

349
