too old fashioned.

362
00:18:39,312 --> 00:18:40,434
The products look old.

363
00:18:40,692 --> 00:18:42,570
But the people look wonderful.

364
00:18:43,976 --> 00:18:46,148
It's a shame we're gonna have
to lop their heads off.

365
00:18:46,312 --> 00:18:48,157
