383
00:20:00,934 --> 00:20:03,377
These two are Carla and Leona.

384
00:20:04,247 --> 00:20:06,972
Not the originals...
it's the third generation.

385
00:20:07,934 --> 00:20:10,395
And what every generation
of Menken dog

386
