when I was nine.

389
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:21,182
So even then you enjoyed
telling men what to do.

390
00:20:22,186 --> 00:20:24,478
To be fair, the store
was practically home.

391
00:20:25,133 --> 00:20:26,660
My father liked to work.

392
00:20:27,872 --> 00:20:29,871
I used to come out here
and talk to them...

393
00:20:30,061 --> 00:20:31,959
Well, the originals... every night.

394
00:20:33,373 --> 00:20:35,987
For a little girl, a dog
can be all you need.

395
00:20:37,123 --> 00:20:39,143
They protect you, they listen.

396
00:20:40,936 --> 00:20:43,292
I had my sister,
but there weren't other kids

397
00:20:44,226 --> 00:20:46,422
and of course,
my mother wasn't around.

398
00:20:47,376 --> 00:20:49,223
Well, that's not always a bad thing.

399
00:20:49,811 --> 00:20:50,811
Who knows?

400
00:20:51,627 --> 00:20:53,559
She died when she was having me.

401
00:20:56,439 --> 00:20:59,126
