415
00:22:41,626 --> 00:22:43,747
I just so looked forward
to seeing you again.

416
00:22:45,502 --> 00:22:46,765
Now I guess that's over.

417
00:23:00,188 --> 00:23:03,556
I know you understand I'd rather
not have to explain this to anyone.

418
00:23:04,813 --> 00:23:06,337
The account stays, I just...

