it was right in the middle
of the news, it was cute.

502
00:30:38,176 --> 00:30:39,693
The guy flying with his hat on.

503
00:30:39,810 --> 00:30:41,783
- Did you do that one?
- It was so cute.

504
00:30:42,376 --> 00:30:44,687
I think the man looks
exactly like Henry.

505
00:30:44,941 --> 00:30:45,941
